item.title: Mom's Tits, Part 1
item.description: I officially became a teenager along with my best friends; Willie, Bubba and Rex, the summer of 1957. Our little pack had formed on the first day of school at Frank Caufield Elementary in third grade. Our families had all moved into the brand new Pleasant Valley subdivision in Chemical City, Texas, a stinking petrochemical town on Karankawa Bay. If we weren’t hanging out at the municipal swimming pool, or wandering around the four block long Main Street business district, we were at my house.
